 regime is much higher than that\nin the rotational excitation regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2017 18:11:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2017 19:56:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-24"}
