ance of\nstate-of-the-art methods on two large public datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2017 05:39:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 4 Mar 2017 07:33:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 27 Mar 2017 00:52:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-28"}
